{"tid":858010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"居安思危","createTime":"2018-10-11T13:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T13:16:43.000Z","uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dec0ddd79eb7e3ebfd547954e40066c61516abde","tid":858010,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/210929_4ae99b635b9672cb9f7af2424a8c5999.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F210929_4ae99b635b9672cb9f7af2424a8c5999.png&h=f13df322&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返秋前算帳真係神作<br />\n<br />\n上網睇到好多人話 唔係一炮過比1.1萬億 係分期<br />\n屌你讀咁多年書讀屎片？<br />\n咁做就係要你唔覺唔覺咁食曬<br />\n好似啲小朋友唔鐘意食紅蘿蔔<br />\n啲屋企人咪磨細粒啲混落啲粥呀飯度比佢地食囉<br />\n你依加覺得無問題？<br />\n到你覺得有問題個陣你已經一無所有"},{"pid":"e87ba2612560c36b1c68ebbb41bb179874fcd525","tid":858010,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"依家個火都開得幾大，已經唔係溫水"},{"pid":"b4f9fb1e3225928d1aebb05332c83bd54ac3018c","tid":858010,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e87ba2612560c36b1c68ebbb41bb179874fcd525","tid":858010,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"依家個火都開得幾大，已經唔係溫水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:16:02.000Z","msg":"依加已經係 見到莞西係隔離唔知做乜"},{"pid":"637137d35c7d0fe8d8394ee329cd42171739fff8","tid":858010,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"點解fb仲咁多人不痛不癢咁？！？！"}]}